import React from 'react';
import { Form, FormField, Button, TextInput, Box } from 'grommet';

function InputForm() {

  return(
    <>
    <Box direction="row" alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'medium' }} pad="medium"> 
      <Form key={1}>
        <FormField label="Requestor">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter Requestor" />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="PR Number">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter PR Number" />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="PO Number">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <Button key={1} type="submit" alignSelf="center" primary label="Submit"  />
      </Form>
    </Box>

    <Box direction="row" alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'medium' }} pad="medium"> 
      <Form key={2}>
        <FormField label="Ship Date">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter Requestor" />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="MAWB">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter PR Number" />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Tracking Number (HAWB/ BL)">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Ship Ref No.">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Carrier">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Arrival Date">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Mode (Courier/Cargo)">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="CAN Date">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="IGM#">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="IGM Date">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <FormField label="Inco-Term(FOB/CIF/EXW/DDP/DAT)">
          <TextInput placeholder="Enter " />
        </FormField>
        <Button key={2} type="submit" alignSelf="center" primary label="Submit"  />
      </Form>
    </Box>

   </> 
  );
}


export default InputForm;
